text: Ðis is sio gerædnes ðe Ælfwold & Eadwold & Æðelflæd geræddan.
<../images/tbar.gif>is<../images/tbar.gif>Æðelflæd & Eadwold geuðen Ælfwolde anes dænnes wið his licwyrðan scætte ðe hio anfeng<../images/tbar.gif>isM CCCC&L denarios.
His terminibus circum jacta ab orientefram ðæm stænenan stapole on Tenet wara brocas .
& on hyring brocasa meridiehyringburne oð æscburnan.
Ab aquilonesia rode fram æscbrygge eft an ðane stænenan stapol.
& se hioræd to sancte Agustine & ða þreo geferscipas innanburhwara & utanburhwara & micle gemettan & Ælfsige burðen.
& Ælfwold gesealde Eadwolde & his sunumCpanæga anuppan all ðis oðer wiððan ðe hit hiora unna wære butan ælcre anwændednesse.
Ðis is hyringdænnes boc ðe Eadwold & Æðelflæd geuðan Ælfwolde wið his licwyrðan scætte.
